### Login (Establish Session)
# @name adminLogin
POST {{API_BASE_URL}}/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "{{TEST_USERNAME}}",
    "password": "{{TEST_USER_PASSWORD}}"
}

###

### List All Permissions (Admin Only)
# Requires ADMIN role
GET {{API_BASE_URL}}/v1/system/permissions
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Check Permission
# Checks if current user has the specified permission
POST {{API_BASE_URL}}/v1/system/permissions/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "permission": "hris.employee.view"
}

###

### Forbidden Test - Non-Admin Access (Expected: 403)
# Use a token from a non-admin user to verify guard works
# GET {{API_BASE_URL}}/system/permissions
# Authorization: Bearer {{nonAdminToken}}
